<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">
<step><![CDATA[1. Peel the potatoes and place them in a bowl of water until you have done them all.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[2. Put the potatoes, water, salt, and vinegar in a pot and bring to boil. Boil high for 10 m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[3. Drain for 5 minutes]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[4. Deep fry in small batches at 200°C for 50 secs, then leave to drain for 30m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[5. When cold freeze, at least overnight]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[6. Deep fry immediatly from frozen at 200°C for 3.5 m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[7. Salt. You can keep warm in wire mesh in oven at 90°C
]]></step>
</directions>
